@DeveloperApi public abstract class WriteAheadLogRecordHandle extends Object implements Serializable
:: DeveloperApi :: This abstract class represents a handle that refers to a record written in a WriteAheadLog. It must contain all the information necessary for the record to be read and returned by an implementation of the WriteAheadLog class.
